.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BALANCE-RATIO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-balance-ratio \- show local/total balance ratio per channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-balance-ratio
.RI [ channel_id ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the ratio of local balance to total capacity for each channel.
A ratio near 0.5 indicates good balance.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, to_us_msat, total_msat, balance_ratio}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-remote-balance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-rebalance-report (1)
